1 Such exempt property C. The property exempt pursuant to this
2 section and subsections K and L of Section 1001 of this title shall
3 remain exempt as long as the property is essential to the production
4 of oil and gas in commercial quantities. The county assessor shall
5 be notified when such property becomes nonexempt.
6 SECTION 2. This act shall become effective January 1, 2027.
